org_similarity_summary.insight_similar_orgs: ALOR, Planet Diamonds, Pamela Love, Gillian Conroy, Marli, and Piranesi are all part of the jewelry retail sector. ALOR, Planet Diamonds, and Gillian Conroy focus on selling a variety of jewelry items including bracelets, earrings, rings, and necklaces. Pamela Love specializes in earrings, necklaces, and bracelets. Marli offers a wide range of jewelry items including pendants, anklets, and rings. Piranesi provides a selection of bracelets, earrings, rings, necklaces, and bridal jewelry.
